					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Unless there's been a shift in terminology in the last couple years: &quot;symbiosis&quot; is the general category of which &quot;mutualism&quot;, &quot;commensalism&quot; and&quot;parasitism&quot; are specifics.</p> 
				 	]]>
