				<wikidot:authorName>SuspiciousScript</wikidot:authorName>				<wikidot:authorUserId>5513975</wikidot:authorUserId>				<content:encoded>
					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Okay, first of all, <em>ew</em>. Disgusted +1.</p> <p>Minor nitpick incoming:</p> <blockquote> <p>SCP-4457-1 instances will then enter a symbiotic relationship with the host.</p> </blockquote> <p>Symbiotic typically means mutually beneficial — this seems more like straight up parasitism.</p> 
				 	]]>
				</content:encoded>							</item>
